Author: iampieman
Text: Same. Like, I’m obese. I recently started obsessively exercising calories off and though “huh, maybe this is an eating disorder” but then thought that if I have the energy to exercise I’m obviously not restricting enough and don’t have a disorder. Plus I’m fat lmao. I feel like a fraud, but still actively participate in all the ED subs...so, I’m like a double fraud? Lma

Author: wispybubble
Text: the fraud feeling never ends. “oh ill feel like i belong when i hit a normal weight!” “oh maybe a BMI of 22 or below.” “definitely will belong when i hit the teens!” annd now i’m like... “will i REALLY have an eating disorder when i hit UW?” 😭
